    //     continuing south-east through Stadshagen → Fridhemsplan →
    //     Rådhuset → T-Centralen → Kungsträdgården.
    //   • T13/T14 share a north trunk through Östermalmstorg before
    //     splitting (T13 NE to Ropsten, T14 N to Mörby centrum), and a
    //     south trunk through T-Centralen → Gamla stan → Slussen →
    //     Mariatorget → Zinkensdamm → Hornstull → Liljeholmen, where
    //     they split SW (T13 via Aspudden/Örnsberg/Axelsberg → Norsborg,
    //     T14 → Fruängen).
    //   • T17/T18/T19 share a horizontal trunk through the city centre.
    //     T19 starts at Hässelby strand, T17 joins at Åkeshov, T18 joins
    //     at Alvik. Together they continue Fridhemsplan → … → T-Centralen
    //     → Gamla stan → Slussen → Medborgarplatsen → Skanstull →
    //     Gullmarsplan, where T19 splits SW. T17/T18 continue to
    //     Skärmarbrink, where T17 branches east (Skarpnäck) and T18
    //     continues south (Farsta strand).
    //
    // Shared stations live at a single canonical (x,y) so polylines
    // actually overlap there. Termini get coloured pills with the line
    // code, central junctions get white pills (T-Centralen, Slussen,
    // Gamla stan, Fridhemsplan).
    // ---------------------------------------------------------------------

    const STATIONS = {
        // ============== BLUE — T10 NORTHERN ARM ==============
        'Hjulsta':              [235,  60],
